Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:41.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No matter where you go, there is nowhere to run! - OG}Podem correr, mas não podem se esconder!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:47.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hakugan, assuma o {\i1}Polar Tang{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:48.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.34,0:01:51.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Shachi! Penguin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.01,0:01:52.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pro mar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:53.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Count on us! - OG}Entendido!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:01.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}Re-Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:12.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What?! - OG}O que é isso?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:17.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Amputate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.80,0:02:32.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's not what I was told he could do! - OG}{No one told me it could do that! - Polly}Não era isso que me disseram que ele podia fazer!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:34.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É uma técnica do despertar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:36.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All right! Fall! - OG}Certo! Cai!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:40.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ainda não!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:45.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn you! - OG}Seu desgraçado!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:48.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Quake Crush!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Maldito monstro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:35.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Gee! - OG}Meu Deus!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:38.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Stronger, você morreu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He was a good guy. - OG}Você foi um bom garoto.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:46.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Take this! - OG}Toma essa!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:54.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What are they?! - OG}O que são essas coisas?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:56.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Saiam da frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:58.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're exploding apples! - OG}Maçãs explosivas!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:21.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What? - OG}Hã?{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:25.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're from an extremely cold port in the North Blue! Screw you! - OG}Não mexam com caras dos\Nportos gelados do North Blue!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:28.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't think you can beat us at sea! - OG}{You can't beat us at sea! - Polly}Vocês não têm chance contra nós no mar!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're gonna sink your ship! - OG}O navio de vocês já era!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(108,0)}Preparar para atacar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:37.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:57.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Jean Bart! Três horas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:59.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um atirador!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:01.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Defend Captain! - OG}Protejam o capitão!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:03.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All right! - OG}Deixa comigo!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Opa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{His guard is tight. - OG}A defesa dele é forte.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}K-Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:33.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That doesn't hurt at all! - OG}{That ain't gonna work! - Polly}Isso nem faz cócegas!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:35.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Shock Wille!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:50.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{See, that's what happens when you charge before you think... - OG}Tá vendo? É isso que acontece\Nquando você avança sem pensar...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:51.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Warp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:56.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Commodore, do you want to go back to the ship? - OG}Comodoro, devemos voltar pro navio?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:06:00.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No way! We'll just keep pushing! - OG}{Are you stupid?\NKeep up the pressure! - Polly}Não seja idiota!\NVamos terminar o que começamos.{LP - TCB}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I see. - OG}Entendido.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:04.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Warp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:18.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Blackbeard! - OG}Barba Negra está aqui!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:20.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All your top officers are power-users! - OG}Todos os seus oficiais são usuários de fruta do diabo?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:27.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That means all of them are weak against the sea! - OG}Isso quer dizer que todos são fracos contra o mar!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:33.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Devil fruits have more advantages than weaknesses! - OG}As vantagens das frutas do diabo\Ncompensam as desvantagens!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:40.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Takt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:49.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}K-Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:56.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{An enemy attack from under the sea! - OG}{Enemies from below! - Polly}Estão atacando por baixo!{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:59.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They wanna sink our ship! - OG}Estão tentando nos afundar!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:02.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No one told me that they're strong while at sea! - OG}Como eles podem ser tão bons na água?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:16.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whew! - OG}Cuidado!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:24.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's shaking due to enemy attacks,\Nbut it'll be over soon. - OG}Só estamos levando uns ataques.\NVai parar de balançar logo.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:27.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Porque nosso comodoro é o mais forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:30.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If Mama were alive, - OG}Se a Mama ainda estiver viva...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:34.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{you wouldn't be able to say such a thing. - OG}vocês não vão falar assim por muito tempo.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:43.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who we're fighting now is the very person who killed Big Mom! - OG}O cara que estamos enfrentando agora\Né quem matou ela!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:48.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If legends are allowed to prevail, the times won't move forward! - OG}Os tempos não vão mudar se\Nas velhas lendas continuarem mandando!{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:51.66,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Cacao Island is one of the islands surrounding the Whole Cake Island. - OG}Na Ilha Cacao,\Nno arquipélago de Whole Cake Island,{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:56.37,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Two intruders came to Chocolat Town where Pudding resided. - OG}dois invasores chegaram a\NChocolat Town, lar de Pudding.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:22.73,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{The intruders' goal was to abduct Pudding. - OG}O objetivo deles era sequestrar Pudding.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.82,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Their identities were... - OG}Os invasores eram...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:29.95,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Van Augur, dos Piratas do Barba Negra...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:31.03,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,e...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.49,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Kuzan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:40.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sei o que vocês\Nquerem que eu faça.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:43.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I won't let you do what you want. - OG}Não vou deixar isso acontecer.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:56.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Black Vortex!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:02.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{[/i1]The Emperor of the Sea Blackbeard and Trafalgar Law clashed at Winner Island in the New World. - OG}{\q2\i1}O Imperador Barba Negra e Trafalgar Law\Nse enfrentaram na Ilha Winner no Novo Mundo!{\i0}{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:05.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I have to wait to see the conclusion again. - OG}De novo, tenho que esperar\Npra ver o resultado.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:09.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's frustrating to be fleet admiral... - OG}Ser almirante da frota é frustrante...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:22.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That pacifista suddenly stopped. - OG}O pacifista parou de repente.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:24.88,Main-207+,,0,0,10,,{Now Bonney... - OG}Agora, Bonney...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:29.47,Main-207+,,0,0,10,,você podia ter me disfarçado com uma idade melhor...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:35.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And I know how you feel, but... - OG}Olha, eu entendo como você se sente, mas...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:40.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{if you don't let us bust up the ones who are not your dad, we'll be in trouble– - OG}se você não deixar a gente bater nos que\Nnão são seu pai, vamos ter problemas–{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Luffy! - OG}Pega leve, Luffy!{Polly - Viz}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpa, Bonney.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:50.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We've been through a lot with the pacifista so... - OG}É que a gente já passou por muita coisa\Ncom esses pacifista, sabe.{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:57.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And turn me back to my original self... - OG}{Also, could you... turn me back to how I was? - Polly}E... me volta pro normal, por favor...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:01.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai, ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:05.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Since they are clones of someone who originally was a human, - OG}Já que são clones de alguém\Nque era originalmente humano,{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:07.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,faz sentido que ele tenha uma família.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:11.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't get offended, Bonney. - OG}{Don't be offended by this, Bonney. - Polly}Não leve a mal, Bonney.{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:17.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What I know about Kuma is that he was an evil king of the Sorbet Kingdom... - OG}Pelo que eu sei, Kuma era\No rei tirano de Sorbet.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:20.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{who was expelled by its citizens, and then became a pirate. - OG}{before his people outed him,\Nand he became a pirate. - Polly}Ele virou pirata depois que\No povo o expulsou.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:22.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{After becoming a member\Nof the Revolutionary Army, - OG}Depois, após se juntar ao Exército Revolucionário,{Polly+Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:26.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{he was arrested by the Marines and sentenced to life. - OG}{he was arrested by the Marines\Nand given a life sentence. - Polly}a Marinha o prendeu\Ne deu prisão perpétua.{Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:33.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But because Vegapunk was deeply interested\Nin his physique and potential, - OG}Mas devido ao fascínio de Vegapunk\Npelo físico e potencial dele,{Polly+Camo+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:37.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,ele pôde voltar ao mar\Ncomo um dos Sete Guerreiros...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:41.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,com a condição de se submeter\Na modificações corporais e clonagem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:43.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Am I wrong? - OG}Estou certo?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:48.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Warlord and cloning parts add up. - OG}A parte do Guerreiro e da clonagem eu entendo.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:50.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But not the cyborg part. - OG}Mas virar um ciborgue?!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:52.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's like the death penalty! - OG}É basicamente uma sentença de morte!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:55.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No one would accept it if they knew that's what it's all about! - OG}Ninguém aceitaria\Nse soubesse o que significa!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:57.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tem razão...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:11:00.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But there are different kinds of life sentences. - OG}Mesmo assim, são muitas condições\Npra uma prisão perpétua.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:03.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wonder what crimes\NKuma the Tyrant committed... - OG}Quão terríveis foram os crimes\Nque Kuma, o Tirano, cometeu...?{LP+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{My father wasn't a tyrant! - OG}Meu pai não era um tirano!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:13.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He didn't like the World Government! - OG}Ele odiava o Governo Mundial!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:15.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's no way he'd cooperate with them! - OG}Ele nunca trabalharia com eles!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:17.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He must've been forcibly modified! - OG}Devem ter modificado ele à força!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:19.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, vocês estão tentando nos matar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:21.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That was close! - OG}Essa foi por pouco!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:24.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{By the way, that was... - OG}A propósito, aquilo era...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:26.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um sabre de luz?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:27.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wow! - OG}Demais!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:30.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é um depósito de sucata...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:32.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{These are the scraps of Vegapunk's inventions. - OG}Deve estar cheio de tralhas do Vegapunk.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.34,0:11:34.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Posso usar isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:39.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, isso é assassinato em nome da ciência!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:56.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{My father said he came from a special tribe. - OG}Meu pai disse que o povo dele é especial.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:11:58.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So what?! - OG}E daí?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não dá o direito deles\Nfazerem experiências com ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:03.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não dá o direito deles de matá-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's true! - OG}É isso aí!{Polly - TCB is perfect here lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A special tribe? - OG}Um povo especial?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:09.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bonney...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:13.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pode me voltar ao normal também?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estamos voando!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:23.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The robot is flying in the sky! - OG}O robô tá voando de verdade!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:31.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This Vegaforce-01 is propelled by the jets on its back, - OG}Este Vegaforce-01 é impulsionado\Npelos jatos nas costas,{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:33.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and kept afloat by an anti-gravity device. - OG}e flutua com uma unidade antigravidade.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:34.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Antigravidade"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:39.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The air conditioning on this island makes it possible, but it may be all over the world someday. - OG}O sistema de climatização da ilha permite isso,\Nmas um dia pode ser global!{Polly - OG is over CPS AND three lines...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:43.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wow! Look at that city! - OG}Uau! Olha essa cidade!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:47.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've never seen buildings like those. - OG}Nunca vi prédios assim.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We'll go higher! - OG}Vamos subir mais!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:59.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, there is a monster! - OG}Olha, um monstro!{Polly - really CR?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:00.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:02.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's a giant robot! - OG}E um robô gigante?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:04.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quantos tem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:05.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Fish are flying! - OG}Os peixes estão voando!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:08.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É por causa da antigravidade?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's a futuristic city! - OG}Que cidade futurista!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's right! - OG}Isso mesmo!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:14.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is an island where the future is made! - OG}{This is the island of tomorrow! - Polly}Nesta ilha, o futuro é agora!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:19.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Future Island, Egghead! - OG}Esta é a Ilha do Futuro, Egghead!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:25.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Above the clouds is the laboratory level, Labophase! - OG}Acima das nuvens fica\No nível do laboratório, a Labophase!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Down there is the factory level, Fabriophase! - OG}E lá embaixo fica\No nível da fábrica, a Fabriophase!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:31.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Workers and researchers live there. - OG}Os trabalhadores e pesquisadores vivem lá.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:34.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Your captain is messing around down there, too. - OG}Parece que o capitão de vocês\Ntá aprontando lá embaixo.{Polly - TCB is too good to not use}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:37.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que bom saber que ele tá bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:46.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're here. - OG}Chegamos!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:49.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't help getting excited! - OG}Mal posso esperar!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:53.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei Zoro, não vem?!\NE você, Brook?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou vigiar o navio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:55.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu também.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:58.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't trust that woman. - OG}Não confio naquela mulher.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:02.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Gee, that fool... - OG}{Man, this guy... - Polly}Cara, esse imbecil...{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:06.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Lilith-chan! You can just forget\Nabout that stupid Moss Head! - OG}Ah, Lilith! Esquece aquele Cabeça de Musgo inútil!{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que é?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Experimenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:11.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Experimentar o quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:16.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The surface is like the Sky Island! - OG}É como a ilha do céu!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:17.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Né?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sério?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:20.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What, what?! - OG}Que isso?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:23.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Interesting! - OG}Que legal!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is so familiar! - OG}Que nostalgia!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah? - OG}Ah, é?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:27.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is the first time for me! - OG}Pra mim é a primeira vez!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's this?! - OG}Que raios é isso?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is this also Vegapunk's handiwork?! - OG}Isso também é obra do Vegapunk?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:33.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes! You guessed right! - OG}Sim! Acertou em cheio!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:37.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{By perfectly controlling the air conditioning on the island, - OG}{By perfectly controlling\Nthe island's atmosphere, - Polly}Ao condicionar precisamente o ar da ilha,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:41.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I was able to modify the density of Pyrobloin and moisture in the condensation nuclei, - OG}eu modifiquei a densidade de pyrobroin\Ne umidade nos núcleos de condensação,{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:44.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and recreate the Island Clouds and Sea Clouds of the Sky Islands! - OG}recriando as nuvens insulares\Ne nuvens marítimas das ilhas do céu!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{My guess wasn't that sophisticated! - OG}Meu palpite não era {\i1}tão{\i0} preciso assim...{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:49.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is the entrance of the lab! - OG}Aqui é a entrada do laboratório!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:50.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:52.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Showy! - OG}Chamativo!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:57.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Change to lab clothes before entering! - OG}{You have to change into\Nlab suits before entering. - Polly}Antes de entrar, vistam os trajes do laboratório!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:00.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Trancos on the sides are changing rooms. - OG}Aquele ali é um trancos, um vestiário!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:03.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bem-vindos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:06.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{[/i1]Choose the clothes you like. - OG}{\i1}Por favor, selecionem o traje de sua preferência.{PP - Egghead 04 19:27}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:08.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The clothes I like... - OG}O traje de minha preferência...{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:16.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's this?! - OG}Que raios é isso?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:19.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Pull the levers on your Dom Shoes yourself. - OG}Testem a alavanca nos sapatos dom.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They'll fit any type of foot! - OG}Servem em qualquer pé!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esses, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:25.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parecem pesados...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.24,0:15:27.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Super leves!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:31.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Cute! - OG}E fofinhos!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:33.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Robin, you look great in them! - OG}Você ficou ótima com isso, Robin!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:34.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ficou perfeito!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:37.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They can strangle a wearer\Nto death if they want! - OG}Essas roupas poderiam esmagar você até a morte!{Poppy - Polly TL note: Robin seems to be saying that, much like the dom shoes we just saw, these clothes can shrink down to fit the wearer and, if they shrunk enough, could strangle you as a result. Robin seems to find this quite amusing}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't say such a scary thing... - OG}Por que você diz coisas tão macabras...?{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:44.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm so excited in these futuristic outfits! - OG}Essas roupas futuristas me deixaram animada!{Polly - mostly Viz}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Vegapunk is impressive! - OG}{Leave it to Vegapunk! - Polly}Mandou bem, Vegapunk!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:48.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Servem perfeitamente até no {\i1}meu{\i0} corpo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:50.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:53.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is just an aloha shirt no matter how you look at it! - OG}A minha é só uma camisa havaiana comum!{Polly - these lines are killing me}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:57.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Nami-san and Robin-chan are cute, so it doesn't matter! - OG}Bom, a Nami e a Robin\Nficaram lindas, então tanto faz!{Polly+Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've never seen this fashion! - OG}Nunca vi moda assim!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:01.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Robin, you look great and strong! - OG}{Robin, that's awesome! You look tough! - Polly}A sua ficou ótima, Robin! Você parece forte!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:02.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como eu fico?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're a pervert no matter what you wear! - OG}Você parece um pervertido com qualquer roupa!{Polly - TCB}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:07.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's too much of a compliment! - OG}Você é muito gentil!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:14.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Gênios conseguem até ver seu próprio futuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:16.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do que você está falando, Vegapunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:18.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I... - OG}{I believe... - Polly}Eu acho...{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:23.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{will die soon... - OG}que vou morrer em breve.{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:24.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop joking! - OG}Chega de piada!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:26.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não tem graça.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:29.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu só queria que você soubesse disso...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:30.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:35.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Didn't you have to go with them? - OG}Você não deveria ter ido com eles?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esta é uma ilha do governo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:40.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who will help them if they get caught? - OG}Quem vai tirar eles de lá\Nse forem pegos?{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:44.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's what I thought. - OG}{Those were my thoughts exactly. - Polly}Era o que eu imaginava.{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:45.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Want some tea? - OG}Aceita um chá?{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:47.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. Thanks. - OG}Claro. Obrigado.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:49.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You misters! - OG}{Gentlemen! - Polly}Meus senhores!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:50.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you still here? - OG}Ainda tá aqui?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:53.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whoa-whoa, wait! - OG}P-Peraí!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:58.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I did get a ride on the condition that the destination would be anywhere outside Wano... - OG}Eu sei que disse que descia\Nem qualquer lugar fora de Wano...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:01.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But not here, mister! - OG}Mas não aqui, meus senhores!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:02.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's a government island! - OG}É uma ilha do governo!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:06.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Thanks for helping our captain. - OG}Soube que ajudou nosso capitão. Valeu.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:06.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Get out. - OG}{Get lost. - Polly}Agora cai fora.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:11.05,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll make these fools pay! - OG}Esses idiotas vão me pagar!{Polly - i feel like this could use an additional sound effect even if there's not one in Toei, maybe a comedic stinger, right now the cut feels a little toothless?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:19.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso parece divertido!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:20.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is fun! - OG}Isso é radical!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:27.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As escadas estão se movendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:30.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The stairs are pouring out from the bottom! - OG}Estão saindo direto do chão!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:35.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qual é o mecanismo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:36.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que alimenta isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:39.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The source of power on this island is fire! - OG}O que move essa ilha é fogo!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:42.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Fire can be converted to all forms of energy. - OG}{You can make any kind of\Nenergy you want with fire. - Polly}Você pode converter fogo em qualquer forma de energia.{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:44.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem muitos recursos aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:47.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've been researching what I should burn. - OG}{I'm always trying to\Nreckon out what burns best. - Polly}Tenho pesquisado o que queima melhor.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:53.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I thought I could even make a sun if only there was a flame that wouldn't go out... - OG}Se houvesse uma chama que não se apagasse,\Neu poderia até criar um sol!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:54.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um sol?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:00.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What?! - OG}Hã?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're walking into a wall! - OG}É uma parede!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:07.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Open it! - OG}Ei, abram!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:09.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What are you doing? Just walk through it! - OG}{What's the hold up? Just walk through it! - Polly}Qual é a demora? É só atravessar!{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't be fooled by what you see. - OG}Não se deixem enganar pelos olhos.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:14.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lilith! Lilith!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Edison?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:21.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Lilith-chan! - OG}Lilith, querida!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não consigo ouvir nada agora–
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O pescoço dele! A cabeça!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:30.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:34.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If his head has been cut off,\Nthere would be a lot of blood. - OG}Se a cabeça tivesse sido cortada,\Nteria sangue pra todo lado.{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:37.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Thanks for a sober analysis! You scare me! - OG}Obrigado pelo comentário!\NNão foi nada assustador!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:39.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji! Você tá bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:40.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:42.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dá pra atravessar normalmente.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:44.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But it doesn't look so... - OG}Não {\i1}parece{\i0} que dá...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:45.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:46.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:47.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vou também.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:48.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Ei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:49.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Bye. - OG}Com licença.{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:52.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I came through... - OG}Eu atravessei...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:53.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:03.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que fizeram isso tão confuso?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:04.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What? - OG}Hã?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:10.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What?! It's just an iron door after we made it through! - OG}O quê?! É só uma porta de ferro deste lado!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:11.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como funciona?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Lilith{-chan} sumiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:16.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Walk straight ahead! - OG}Sigam em frente!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:18.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Huh? Who is it? - OG}Hã? Quem é?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm Vegapunk Edison! - OG}Meu nome é Vegapunk Edison!{Polly - TL note: Edison uses a Kyoto/Osaka dialect, which I'm going for Doug Dimmadome, owner of the Dimmsdale Dimmadome/oil baron voice on}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:22.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm glad you made it. - OG}Que bom que vieram.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Just follow my lead. - OG}Sigam-me!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:30.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Still straight ahead. - OG}Só mais um pouco.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:32.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que será que tem pela frente.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:35.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I gotta hunt for "future treasure"! - OG}Hora de procurar o tesouro do futuro!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:37.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's "future treasure"? - OG}O que é "tesouro do futuro"?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:40.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tipo flores feitas de pedras preciosas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:43.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não sei se é infantil ou antiquado...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:45.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Future Kick!{OG}{Polly - wow, solid english hard K sound from nami's VA here}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:01.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem alguém ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:04.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What?! - OG}Hã?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:05.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:08.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Jinbe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:10.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But he's too young. - OG}É jovem demais.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:12.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And he looks different. - OG}E parece diferente.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:20.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The first possibility. Jinbe's child! - OG}Possibilidade um: é filho do Jinbe!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:25.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The second possibility. Jinbe was turned into a child! - OG}Possibilidade dois: o Jinbe foi transformado {\i1}em{\i0} criança!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:26.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:29.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The third possibility. Jinbe's look-alike! - OG}Possibilidade três: é o sósia do Jinbe!{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:31.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tem asas...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:33.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And he has a strange vibe... - OG}e uma energia estranha...{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:36.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Quem é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:43.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He looks like a kid, but as big as Jinbe! - OG}Parece uma criança, mas é do tamanho do Jinbe!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:45.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I have a bad feeling! - OG}Tenho um mau pressentimento...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:48.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The fourth possibility! - OG}Possibilidade quatro!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:50.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A Pacifista! - OG}É um pacifista!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:15.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is a set-up! - OG}Era uma armadilha!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:18.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I knew that the government wouldn't welcome us! - OG}Eu sabia que o governo\Nnão seria tão hospitaleiro!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:20.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Para, Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:25.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele não reage a esse nome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:28.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Does that mean he's Jinbe's clone?! - OG}Então ele é um clone do Jinbe?{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:35.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's not that simple! - OG}Isso não facilita as coisas!{LP+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:38.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I even hesitate to attack him just because he's a kid! - OG}E eu não vou sair batendo em criança!{Z}
Comment: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:46.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?!{OG}{Polly - no way this needs a sub lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:47.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is he a power user?! - OG}Ele é um usuário de fruta?!{Polly+Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:51.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que tá acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:55.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que quer fazer, Nami?!\NQuer lutar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:57.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera, Zeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:01.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! You've got to be kidding! - OG}Ei! Peraí!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:03.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele poder é da...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:12.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.82,0:22:20.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Para!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.49,0:22:25.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Jinbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:27.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu maldito! Solta a Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:29.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:33.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll make you pay even if\NVegapunk is responsible for this! - OG}Obra do Vegapunk ou não,\Nvocê vai pagar!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:35.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay, death penalty it is! - OG}Certo! Pena de morte!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.38,0:22:38.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even if you're... - OG}Mesmo que você seja...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:40.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Jinbe! - OG}o verdadeiro Jinbe!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.77,0:22:53.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I feel the same as them! - OG}Concordo.{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:55.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você fez é imperdoável!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.65,0:22:57.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gigante Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:09.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Sea Serpent Snapdragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:19.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Spank!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:27.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sai da frente, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:33.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He uses the Fishman Karate, too! - OG}Ele usa karatê dos homens-peixe também?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.10,0:23:35.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Lethal Green Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.94,0:23:38.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Skull Bombgrass!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.44,0:23:47.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even though I know he's not Jinbe, I'm reluctant to do this! - OG}Mesmo sabendo que não é o Jinbe,\Nnão me sinto bem com isso!{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.82,0:23:51.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Did it get him?! - OG}Funcionou?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.16,0:23:53.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, I think it did! - OG}Acho que sim!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:23:59.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele sumiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.42,0:24:01.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sumiu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.04,0:24:02.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.17,0:24:04.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He got hit, didn't he?! - OG}Eu acertei ele, não acertei?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.18,0:24:14.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.43,0:24:16.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me solta!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:17.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!{OG}{Polly - ARE YOU FOR REAL LMAO}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.89,0:24:19.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji, deixa comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.27,0:24:23.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp, não se mexe!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.36,0:24:30.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desgraçado! Me solta!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.53,0:24:33.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I said "Don't move"! - OG}Eu disse pra não se mexer!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.20,0:24:37.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquela energia...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.33,0:24:38.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't tell me it's... - OG}O que diabos...?{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.75,0:24:41.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Radical...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.46,0:24:43.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Desvia, S-Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.88,0:24:45.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.89,0:24:57.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He used a laser beam! - OG}Ele usou um raio laser!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.48,0:24:58.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who is he?! - OG}Quem é esse cara?!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.85,0:25:01.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{[/an8]And it was extremely high power! - OG}{\an8}E é potente pra caramba!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.56,0:25:03.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{[/an8]That was close! - OG}{\an8}Essa foi por pouco!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.19,0:25:06.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{The seraphim is still a child. He's not ready for a laser beam experiment yet! - OG}O seraphim ainda é uma criança!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.69,0:25:08.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ele não tá pronto pra um experimento\Nde laser ainda!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.53,0:25:10.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's right! - OG}Com certeza!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.36,0:25:13.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quanto será que custa um seraphim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.32,0:25:16.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That fool! Should I rip his head off?! - OG}Vou arrancar a cabeça desse idiota!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.04,0:25:17.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're evil! - OG}Que maldade!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.58,0:25:19.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's no need to show pirates any mercy! - OG}Não mostrem nenhuma misericórdia a piratas!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.46,0:25:23.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna make this place their graveyard! - OG}Vou enterrá-los bem aqui!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.46,0:25:25.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're devilish! - OG}Que {\i1}muita{\i0} maldade!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.21,0:25:28.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{S-Shark, beat them thoroughly! - OG}S-Shark, acaba com eles!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.30,0:25:30.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Kick their asses! - OG}Dá uma bela surra neles!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.22,0:25:31.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já chega!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.84,0:25:34.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não ia chegar a {\i1}esse{\i0} ponto!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.30,0:25:38.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, I got an idea for a new invention! - OG}Eureka! Tive uma ideia pra uma nova invenção!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.39,0:25:40.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, yeah? - OG}Ah, é?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.02,0:25:42.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then leave everything to me from now! - OG}Então deixa comigo daqui em diante!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.27,0:25:43.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixo o resto com você...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.77,0:25:44.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pythagoras!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.61,0:25:45.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What?! - OG}Como é?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.65,0:25:46.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Claro!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.65,0:25:50.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Interesting battle data like this is hard to get! - OG}Dados de combate interessantes\Nassim não aparecem todo dia!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.62,0:25:56.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I have to draw blueprints now! - OG}Preciso desenhar os projetos!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.87,0:25:58.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tanta coisa, tanta coisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.12,0:26:00.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'd welcome even a cat's help! - OG}Aceitaria até ajuda de um gato nesse ponto!{Polly - lol, Viz calls the cat an "assis-tabby"}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.63,0:26:09.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Maravilhoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.26,0:26:12.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yay! - OG}Excelente!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.93,0:26:16.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os padrões de ataque do seraphim\Nestão evoluindo conforme ele cresce!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.60,0:26:21.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Does that mean experiences get stored\Nin their hereditary elements as I thought? - OG}Será que isso confirma minha teoria de que experiências\Nsão armazenadas nos elementos hereditários?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.18,0:26:22.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.31,0:26:24.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Really give it to them! - OG}Manda ver neles!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.23,0:26:26.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.77,0:26:31.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{His accelerated growth allows him to solve problems! - OG}Isso pode ser a solução para\No problema do crescimento acelerado!{Polly - In a rare upset, CR mistranslated this; went back and forth with Jaz and LP on this, but this is apparently the correct interpretation; he's saying that the lineage factor is the solution to the problem }
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.53,0:26:35.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{From a heart rate of 90 BPM, green blood concentration went up! - OG}Frequência cardíaca acima de 90 BPM!\NO sangue verde está fluindo mais rápido!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.54,0:26:43.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Show them your true power! - OG}Mostra do que você é feito!{Polly}
Comment: 0,0:26:38.54,0:26:43.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Show them your true power!
Comment: 0,0:26:40.87,0:26:43.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Show them your true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.10,0:27:02.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quanto mais eu escrevo...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.23,0:27:04.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mais meu estômago ronca!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.15,0:27:07.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't stop the ideas from coming! - OG}As ideias não param de vir!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.81,0:27:09.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't have time to eat! - OG}Não tenho tempo de comer!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.40,0:27:12.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Eat something for me, York! - OG}Preciso que coma por mim, York!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.78,0:27:16.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.12,0:27:23.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Here it comes! Nutrition is soaking into my brain! - OG}É isso aí! Os nutrientes estão\Nchegando no meu cérebro!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.54,0:27:25.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I got even more ideas! - OG}Tive ainda mais ideias!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.96,0:27:29.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Come! Come! York!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.75,0:27:33.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Here's more food! York-sama! - OG}Mais uma porção pra você, Dra. York.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.01,0:27:40.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's not enough! - OG}Não é suficiente!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.01,0:27:41.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me tragam mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.76,0:27:44.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes, ma'am! Right away! - OG}Sim, doutora! Imediatamente!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.32,0:27:54.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Gostoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.61,0:27:57.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O IMC atual dela passou de 600!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.57,0:27:59.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't want more! - OG}Não quero mais!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.78,0:28:02.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É isso aí, S-Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.99,0:28:06.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Battle data keeps getting updated! - OG}Os dados de combate continuam atualizando!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.88,0:28:11.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Not now...! - OG}Ah não, agora não...!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.17,0:28:19.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ow, ow, ow... Let's call a temporary truce! - OG}Ai, ai... Vou declarar uma trégua temporária!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.64,0:28:22.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't want to miss his growth! - OG}Não posso perder essa oportunidade\Nde monitorar o crescimento dele!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.72,0:28:26.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wanna go to the bathroom,\Nbut I don't wanna waste any time! - OG}Preciso ir ao banheiro,\Nmas não posso perder tempo!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.57,0:28:35.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I feel much better! - OG}{\pos(300,1053)}Muito melhor!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.57,0:28:35.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I feel much better! - OG}{\pos(950,1053)}Muito melhor!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.57,0:28:35.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I feel much better! - OG}{\pos(1616,1053)}Muito melhor!{Polly}
Comment: 0,0:28:35.28,0:28:36.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,The sound effect for the previous shot cuts off a little harshly, if it's possible to do anything about it{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.95,0:28:40.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Digestion Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.28,0:28:45.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's done! Let's do an experiment! - OG}Pronto! Hora de experimentar!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.41,0:28:48.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Could you bring me all materials on devil fruits?! - OG}Por favor, tragam todos os materiais\Nrelacionados a frutas do diabo!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.37,0:28:51.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Bring all materials to Pythagoras-sama! - OG}Entreguem tudo ao Dr. Pythagoras!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.00,0:28:52.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Prepare for Mr. Edison's experiment! - OG}Preparem pro experimento do Dr. Edison!{Polly - TL note: so, there is actually a different honorific being used here, -shi, which is used mostly by the media to refer to persons of interest, such as Baiden-shi (Joe Biden). still, given the context, it's more consistent to translate this as Dr. rather than Mr.}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.75,0:28:55.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Para a sala de simulação 88!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.63,0:28:57.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sleepy. - OG}Hora de dormir.{Polly - stole this one from WF in arlong park heh heh}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.59,0:29:04.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's York-sama's fourth Kuu Dasu Neru (Eat Poop Sleep) today! - OG}Esse é o quarto ciclo de\Ncomer, evacuar e dormir da Dra. York hoje!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.77,0:29:15.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You've got to be kidding! - OG}Tá brincando?!{Polly - the shot of his legs is literally insane, is it upside down in the toei version too? i guess it's franky POV, lol?}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.08,0:29:25.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já chega, seraphim.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.91,0:29:26.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Retreat. - OG}Recuem.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.79,0:29:29.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Edison, Lilith, Pythagoras!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.33,0:29:31.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acho que já foi o suficiente.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.75,0:29:33.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, que pena...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.84,0:29:35.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn! - OG}Droga!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.59,0:29:36.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.96,0:29:38.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's wrong with that bastard?! - OG}Por que esse desgraçado tá se metendo?!{LP+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.63,0:29:40.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We were just getting to the best part! - OG}Estávamos chegando na melhor parte!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.68,0:29:42.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I got an idea! - OG}Eureka!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.35,0:29:54.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Did he come to help us?! - OG}Ele veio nos salvar?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.23,0:29:56.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's shady no matter how you look at him! - OG}Nada disso, ele é tão suspeito\Nquanto os outros!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.61,0:29:59.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Looks like he's Lilith's colleague. - OG}Deve ser um colega da Lilith.{Polly - LP thinks colleague is too impersonal, but neither of us has a better word here}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.11,0:30:01.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then maybe he's also... - OG}Então esse cara deve ser...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.61,0:30:04.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm Dr. Vegapunk Shaka. - OG}Eu sou o Dr. Vegapunk Shaka.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.87,0:30:10.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mais um?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.50,0:30:12.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que há com vocês?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.83,0:30:15.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So you guys are the Straw Hats. - OG}Vocês devem ser os Piratas do Chapéu de Palha.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.17,0:30:17.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! What's wrong with these shoes?! - OG}Somos! Agora me diz o que\Nhá de errado com esses sapatos!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.63,0:30:19.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estão grudados no chão!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.59,0:30:23.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Dom Shoes can always be controlled easily by the power of magnets in the lab. - OG}Sapatos dom podem ser facilmente controlados\Npelos ímãs do laboratório.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.97,0:30:25.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I guess it's no use to resist. - OG}Então resistir é inútil.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.43,0:30:28.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não podemos confiar em piratas.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.93,0:30:33.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There was a female Vegapunk and a Vegapunk who was talking through speakers. - OG}{\q2}Também tinha uma Vegapunk mulher,\Ne outra que falava por alto-falantes...{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.77,0:30:34.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.81,0:30:36.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I am Vegapunk, too. - OG}Eu também sou Vegapunk.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.86,0:30:38.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não entendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.73,0:30:40.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quantos de vocês existem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.24,0:30:42.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Talvez {\i1}eu{\i0} também seja Vegapunk...{OG}{Polly - are there any OTHER vegapunks i should know about?}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.49,0:30:43.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.49,0:30:46.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, you're not! - OG}É claro que não!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.66,0:30:54.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Does this island look like the future to you guys? - OG}Esta ilha parece o futuro\Npra vocês?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.37,0:30:56.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, é incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.88,0:30:58.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's not just an ordinary future. - OG}Não é um futuro qualquer!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.38,0:31:00.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Those mechanical sea beasts! - OG}Tinha aquelas bestas marinhas mecânicas!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.13,0:31:04.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Vegaforce-01 and air-conditioning on the island, too! - OG}Mais o Vegaforce-01\Ne o sistema de climatização!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.88,0:31:06.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É um futuro e tanto!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.93,0:31:09.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E nunca vi uma cidade assim...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.89,0:31:14.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wanna look around and see what kind of technology is used! - OG}Quero bisbilhotar\Ne ver como tudo funciona!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.89,0:31:16.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't say that we're enemies! - OG}{We don't have to fight! - Polly}Não seja tão frio!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.65,0:31:19.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's be friends, Vega-chan! - OG}Vamos ser amigos, Vega!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.65,0:31:22.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There is something that even I can't surpass. - OG}Até minha tecnologia ainda está tão atrás...{Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.95,0:31:27.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esta ilha é do passado.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.62,0:31:29.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.41,0:31:32.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como assim "do passado"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.66,0:31:35.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{For example, if I said... - OG}E se eu dissesse...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.08,0:31:41.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...there was an advanced kingdom like Eggheadd 900 years ago, - OG}que 900 anos atrás, existia\Num reino avançado como Egghead...?{Polly - by the way, that typo really is in the original line}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.71,0:31:43.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{would you believe it? - OG}Vocês acreditariam?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.97,0:31:46.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{900 years ago?! - OG}Novecentos anos atrás?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.88,0:31:48.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Do que você está falando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.18,0:31:55.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is real! - OG}É real!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.81,0:31:57.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olha, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.44,0:31:59.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é um holograma!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.02,0:32:01.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá ali de verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.44,0:32:02.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É feito de ferro!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.70,0:32:07.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.11,0:32:08.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá bem acabado.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.41,0:32:11.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Did it used to work? - OG}Será que já funcionou?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.87,0:32:15.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Only technology of the future could make it work... - OG}{Only technology of\Nthe future could make it run... - Polly}Isso exigiria tecnologia futurista.{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.00,0:32:16.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é velho demais?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.83,0:32:18.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu quero subir nele!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.58,0:32:20.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, let's ride it! - OG}É, vamos subir!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.59,0:32:22.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos, Chopper!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=74}===============================DIALOGUE============================
